  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The property is highly visible from Upper Street and Florence Street and the loss of the butterfly roof profile and the proposed mansard roof extension would be harmful to the architectural character and integrity of the subject property and would disrupt the general uniformity of the terrace to the detriment of the wider Upper Street (North) Conservation Area.  The proposal would therefore fail to comply with policies D3, D4, D11 and D25 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan (2002) and the requirements of the Conservation Area Design Guide (2002) and the Islington Urban Design Guide (2006)."
